{"tid":2332483,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"邊條撚樣以後再話龍門難食嘅話，一律當做係渣家軍(JJJ)處理！","createTime":"2020-12-19T15:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T01:34:08.000Z","uid":73381,"like":15,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8039a0323e7276334c5e8d516f445f5107cb104a","tid":2332483,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEicNTuk.jpg&amp;h=457a6da6&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真 依家龍門已經進步咗好多 仲話佢難食嗰班撚樣我估似係收咗渣家軍(JJJ)錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相<br />\n<br />\n塊朱扒有醃過 唔會太柴太瘦 圖都可以見到有少少肥肉 仲要有炸過同埋大大舊 加埋兩條香腸 個人覺得比龍門居其他茶餐廳好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好人話唔好食你就執人口水尾好無？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wvd6bxH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvd6bxH.jpg&h=82f3cc2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hNbnEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hNbnEm.jpg&h=f6b894df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e341b34e85c0f85b4e294d4f33fae957edf197b5","tid":2332483,"uid":73381,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤(杜狗)條撚樣成日陰啲陰啲串鳩龍門難食 又宣傳藍店KFC 100%似係收咗渣家軍(JJJ)錢<br />\n<br />\n而所有渣家軍嘅人 連登仔一律建議當藍處理<br />\n<br />\n杜狗呢條深藍賤畜 我地寧願中共管治香港都想佢死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0df122d14f1e81dfab7532c13642cbb59db565","tid":2332483,"uid":261505,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:53:40.000Z","msg":"修煉饅頭的秘方<br />\n店內播放榮光歸香港<br />\n奶茶淡如清水 照樣賣清光 <br />\n消失了的月餅　懇請你的原諒 <br />\n為一盒五仁養一身傷<br />\n別想投訴我 我會告手足誹謗 <br />\n<br />\n作詞：死雞樂"},{